description:
This application offers a free bare
bones api to Google Maps.  Since Google Maps charges fees for developers using their maps api in their paid application, I have created a free app that you can launch from your application, passing in some basic input parameters to use Google maps api for free.  Download this application and read the help for further instructions.  This app is intended for developers only.  You can see a sample map generated by this app in the screenshots.
versionNote: 1.0.1 Bug Fix - Specified Google Maps Version to show icons consistently
